Peaked Circuits solver — third-party code attribution
=====================================================

This solution vendors, VERBATIM, the following source files from:

    Efficient Classical Simulation of Heuristic Peaked Quantum Circuits
    David Kremer and Nicolas Dupuis (IBM T.J. Watson Research Center)
    arXiv:2604.21908
    https://github.com/d-kremer/peaked-circuit-simulation
    Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0 (see LICENSE-Apache-2.0).

Vendored files (unmodified):
    utils.py         — circuit layering, TNO contraction, MPS sampling, marginal
                       bitstring extraction, amplitude (bitstring_probability)
    circuit_mpo.py   — MPO construction from circuits, MPO-MPO composition, swaps
    unswap.py        — MPO iterative cancellation with greedy "unswapping",
                       rewiring, and adaptive side selection

The method targets the peaked circuits of:

    Heuristic Quantum Advantage with Peaked Circuits
    Gharibyan et al. (BlueQubit), arXiv:2510.25838
    https://arxiv.org/abs/2510.25838

